title: *** FLASH FLOOD DISCONTINUED FOR ALL PARISHES *** (Meteorological Service of Jamaica)
text: ( Source : Meteorological Service of Jamaica ) The Meteorological Service has discontinued. • A Flash Flood Watch for low-lying and flood prone areas of eastern and south-central parishes. • Effective 5:00 p.m. Sunday. Meanwhile … **** RAGGED
